134 4. The person listing the property shall enter a true
135 and correct statement of the property, in a printed blank
136 prepared for that purpose. The statement, after being
137 filled out, shall be signed and either affirmed or sworn to
138 as provided in section 137.155. The list shall then be
139 delivered to the assessor.
140 5. (1) All subclasses of real property, as such
141 subclasses are established in Section 4(b) of Article X of
142 the Missouri Constitution and defined in section 137.016,
143 shall be assessed at the following percentages of true value
144 for all calendar years ending on or before December 31,

